    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/e078b729f0cb83e947d2ac54ea6f3c79.poster.avif?t=1746826625\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/e078b729f0cb83e947d2ac54ea6f3c79.webm?t=1746826625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/e078b729f0cb83e947d2ac54ea6f3c79.mp4?t=1746826625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Welcome aboard the most luxurious cruise ship ever to sail the oceans! In the &quot;Cruise Ship&quot; DLC for Thief Simulator 2, you take on the role of a thief embarking on a new, exciting mission. This time, your target is a massive cruise ship full of wealthy passengers and valuable treasures waiting to be stolen. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/93d53bf11480c09ad029450409cf174b.poster.avif?t=1746826625\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/93d53bf11480c09ad029450409cf174b.webm?t=1746826625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/93d53bf11480c09ad029450409cf174b.mp4?t=1746826625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immerse yourself in a world of opulence, where every corner of the ship hides secrets. From luxurious suites to hidden storage rooms and engine rooms – you'll find something valuable worth stealing everywhere you look! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/806bd3539fa8763ca65558d244efa65a.poster.avif?t=1746826625\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/806bd3539fa8763ca65558d244efa65a.webm?t=1746826625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/806bd3539fa8763ca65558d244efa65a.mp4?t=1746826625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this DLC, you will find:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A completely new location with shops, gyms, suites, pools, and more</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New story missions that will immerse you in the atmosphere of luxurious tropics</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New valuable items waiting to be looted</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Motorboats and small boats</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >New jobs</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/a83a716075d0b0eb78507f34f312b368.poster.avif?t=1746826625\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/a83a716075d0b0eb78507f34f312b368.webm?t=1746826625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/a83a716075d0b0eb78507f34f312b368.mp4?t=1746826625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Do you have what it takes to pull off the perfect heist in the middle of the ocean? &quot;Thief Simulator 2: Cruise Ship&quot; is your ticket to a world of risk and wealth. Get ready for the most exciting heist of your life!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/94b56d4d872ad8d5e0125641f7958f06.poster.avif?t=1746826625\" width=800 height=292 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/94b56d4d872ad8d5e0125641f7958f06.webm?t=1746826625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3027860/extras/94b56d4d872ad8d5e0125641f7958f06.mp4?t=1746826625\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
